tasks.description:
Add an 'Export Chat' button (download icon) to the interview tab header in frontend/src/views/AgentProfileView.vue. When clicked, generate a markdown-formatted file containing the full interview conversation. Format: `# Interview with {Agent Name}

**Role:** {role}
**Company:** {company}
**Date:** {ISO date}

---

` followed by each Q&A pair as `### Q: {question}

> {agent response}

`. Use the Blob API to create the file and trigger a download with filename `interview-{agent-name-slugified}-{date}.md`. Include a metadata section at the top with simulation ID, total questions asked, and interview duration. If no interview messages exist, disable the button and show a tooltip 'Start an interview first'. Also add a 'Copy to Clipboard' option that copies the same markdown to the clipboard with a toast confirmation.
